### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los huéspedes (protegido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener huésped por ID (protegido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guests/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un nuevo huésped (protegido)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/guests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Lopez (Protected)",
  "documentNumber": "987654321",
  "phone": "3109876543",
  "email": "maria.protected@example.com"
}

### Actualizar un huésped (protegido)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/guests/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "3205551234"
}

### Eliminar lógicamente un huésped (protegido)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/guests/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}